  - Title: Qur’ân
    Location: XXV 70
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Work, Action and Society=On ‘Karma’ and ‘Karma Yoga’
---
Who repenteth and believeth and doth righteous work： as for such,
Allâh will change Faith their evil deeds to good deeds. Allâh is ever
Forgiving, Merciful.
